Emix
<font face=aircut3/18 color=#88eeff>
<p align=50%>
Simple audio mixer
<font face=aircut3/12 color=#ffffff>
<p align=50%>
(c) 1999 Roberto Machorro
<p>
There are four channels in this mixer, with them you can adjust the output volume of several devices. Each slider is a device, they are (from left to right): Master Volume, Synth Volume, PCM Volume and CD Audio Volume.
<p>
The buttons actions are (from top to botton): Close the Epplet, Mute all audio and Display this help.
<p>
